            <h2>Setup Instructions</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>
                    <p>Clone the repository:</p>
                    <code>git clone https://github.com/antonmironovv/TelerikDataMind-Public.git</code><br>
                    <code>cd TelerikDataMind-Public</code>
                </li>
                <li>Open the solution in Visual Studio.</li>
                <li>Restore NuGet packages: <code>dotnet restore</code></li>
                <li>
                    <p>Add Telerik NuGet feed:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Go to <strong>Tools → Options → NuGet Package Manager → Package Sources</strong></li>
                        <li>Add: <code>https://nuget.telerik.com/v3/index.json</code></li>
                        <li>Authenticate with your Telerik credentials.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Insert your OpenAI <strong>ApiKey</strong> and <strong>DeploymentName</strong> in the <code>appsettings.json</code>.</li>
                <li>Run the project: <code>dotnet run</code></li>
                <li>Open your browser.</li>
            </ol>
            
